4530.web.pdf" rel="nofollow">http://www.journals.uchicago.edu/AJHG/journal/issues/v72n3/024530/024530.web.pdf</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=The+Genetic+Legacy+of+the+Mongols&amp;rft.jtitle=The+American+Journal+of+Human+Genetics&amp;rft.aulast=Zerjal%2C+Xue%2C+Bertorelle%2C+Wells%2C+Bao%2C+Zhu%2C+Qamar%2C+Ayub%2C+Mohyuddin%2C+Fu%2C+Li%2C+Yuldasheva%2C+Ruzibakiev%2C+Xu%2C+Shu%2C+Du%2C+Yang%2C+Hurles%2C+Robinson%2C+Gerelsaikhan%2C+Dashnyam%2C+Mehdi%2C+Tyler-Smith&amp;rft.au=Zerjal%2C+Xue%2C+Bertorelle%2C+Wells%2C+Bao%2C+Zhu%2C+Qamar%2C+Ayub%2C+Mohyuddin%2C+Fu%2C+Li%2C+Yuldasheva%2C+Ruzibakiev%2C+Xu%2C+Shu%2C+Du%2C+Yang%2C+Hurles%2C+Robinson%2C+Gerelsaikhan%2C+Dashnyam%2C+Mehdi%2C+Tyler-Smith&amp;rft.date=2003&amp;rft.volume=72&amp;rft.issue=72&amp;rft.pages=717%E2%80%93721%3B&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1086%2F367774&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.journals.uchicago.edu%2FAJHG%2Fjournal%2Fissues%2Fv72n3%2F024530%2F024530.web.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Genghis_Khan"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
