<td><a href="/wiki/Tem%C3%BCr_Khan,_Emperor_Chengzong_of_Yuan" title="Temür Khan, Emperor Chengzong of Yuan">Oljei Temur Khagan</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/K%C3%BCl%C3%BCg_Khan,_Emperor_Wuzong_of_Yuan" title="Külüg Khan, Emperor Wuzong of Yuan">Khayisan Khulug</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Ayurbarwada_Buyantu_Khan,_Emperor_Renzong_of_Yuan" title="Ayurbarwada Buyantu Khan, Emperor Renzong of Yuan">Buyantu Ayurbarwada</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Gegeen_Khan,_Emperor_Yingzong_of_Yuan" title="Gegeen Khan, Emperor Yingzong of Yuan">Gegeen Khagan Shidebala</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Yes%C3%BCn_Tem%C3%BCr_Khan,_Emperor_Taiding_of_Yuan" title="Yesün Temür Khan, Emperor Taiding of Yuan">Yesün Temür Khagan</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Ragibagh_Khan,_Emperor_Tianshun_of_Yuan" title="Ragibagh Khan, Emperor Tianshun of Yuan">Ragibagh Khan</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Jayaatu_Khan,_Emperor_Wenzong_of_Yuan" title="Jayaatu Khan, Emperor Wenzong of Yuan">Jayaatu Khagan Tugh-Temur</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Khutughtu_Khan,_Emperor_Mingzong_of_Yuan" title="Khutughtu Khan, Emperor Mingzong of Yuan">Khutughtu Khagan Quselan</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Rinchinbal_Khan,_Emperor_Ningzong_of_Yuan" title="Rinchinbal Khan, Emperor Ningzong of Yuan">Rinchinbal</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Ukhaantu_Khan,_Emperor_Huizong_of_Yuan" title="Ukhaantu Khan, Emperor Huizong of Yuan">Ukhaantu Khan Toghan-Temur</a></td>
