<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em">
<div>
<p><small><b>Early Mongol rulers posthumously promoted by</b> <a href="/wiki/Kublai_Khan" title="Kublai Khan">Kublai Khan</a> <b>as Yuan emperors</b><br />
<strong class="selflink">Genghis Khan</strong> <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Tolui" title="Tolui">Tolui Khan</a> <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/%C3%96gedei_Khan" title="Ögedei Khan">Ögedei Khan</a> <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/G%C3%BCy%C3%BCk_Khan" title="Güyük Khan">Güyük Khan</a> <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/M%C3%B6ngke_Khan" title="Möngke Khan">Möngke Khan</a><br />
<br /></small> <b>Following conquest of <a href="/wiki/Southern_Song" title="Southern Song" class="mw-redirect">Southern Song</a> Dynasty in 1279 as <i><a href="/wiki/Emperor_of_China" title="Emperor of China">Emperor of China</a></i>, along with their original title <a href="/wiki/Khagan" title="Khagan">Khagan</a> of the Mongols</b><br />
<a href="/wiki/Kublai_Khan" title="Kublai Khan">Kublai Khan</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Tem%C3%BCr_Khan,_Emperor_Chengzong_of_Yuan" title="Temür Khan, Emperor Chengzong of Yuan">Chengzong</a> <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/K%C3%BCl%C3%BCg_Khan,_Emperor_Wuzong_of_Yuan" title="Külüg Khan, Emperor Wuzong of Yuan">Wuzong</a> <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Ayurbarwada_Buyantu_Khan,_Emperor_Renzong_of_Yuan" title="Ayurbarwada Buyantu Khan, Emperor Renzong of Yuan">Renzong</a> <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Gegeen_Khan,_Emperor_Yingzong_of_Yuan" title="Gegeen Khan, Emperor Yingzong of Yuan">Yingzong</a> <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Yes%C3%BCn_Tem%C3%BCr_Khan,_Emperor_Taiding_of_Yuan" title="Yesün Temür Khan, Emperor Taiding of Yuan">Taiding Di</a> <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Ragibagh_Khan,_Emperor_Tianshun_of_Yuan" title="Ragibagh Khan, Emperor Tianshun of Yuan">Tianshun Di</a> <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Jayaatu_Khan,_Emperor_Wenzong_of_Yuan" title="Jayaatu Khan, Emperor Wenzong of Yuan">Wenzong</a> <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Khutughtu_Khan,_Emperor_Mingzong_of_Yuan" title="Khutughtu Khan, Emperor Mingzong of Yuan">Mingzong</a> <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Rinchinbal_Khan,_Emperor_Ningzong_of_Yuan" title="Rinchinbal Khan, Emperor Ningzong of Yuan">Ningzong</a> <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Ukhaatu_Khan,_Emperor_Huizong_of_Yuan" title="Ukhaatu Khan, Emperor Huizong of Yuan" class="mw-redirect">Huizong</a></p>
</div>
